# kart.start with an empty name fails with code:2 invalid_flag before any
# devpod subprocess spawns. Proves the Register wiring landed and that
# bindLifecycleParams' empty-name guard is applied uniformly.

stdin start.json
lakitu rpc
! stderr .
stdout '"error":'
stdout '"code":2'
stdout '"type":"invalid_flag"'

-- start.json --
{"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"kart.start","params":{"name":""},"id":1}
